quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,35,"O naati ka ngesa makko tawi ko o tooñɗo hoore-makko, o wi'i: "Mi sikkaani ba re'ay poomaa"."
  18,36,"Mi sikkaani kadai Darnga ngal daroto, mi wooɗndii si mi artira le ka Joomi am, maa mi taw sanne, waylitorde ɓurnde ba moƴƴude."
  18,37,"Gon'diijo o makko on wi'i mo, tawi homo yewtude mo: "Enee, a yeddii On Takɗo ma immorde mbullaari=leydi refti e toɓɓere [maniiyu] refti O fotndumaa gorko"."
  18,38,"Kono min ko Kaŋko Alla woni Joomi am, mi kafidataa e Joomi am hay gooto."
  18,39,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde naatuɗaa ka ngesa maaɗa mbi'aa: "Ko Alla muuyi ko doole alaa si wanaa Alla". Si a yi'ii kam min miɗo ɓurmaa famɗude jawdi e ɓiɗɓe."
  18,40,"No jortaa nde Joomi am okkoyta kam moƴƴere ɓurnde ngesa maa ba O nula e mabba lepte immorde ka kammu ba wonta boowal ɓowrungal."
  18,41,"Maa de ndiyam mabba ɗa wonta ɓeeɓuɗam, hara a hattantaa ɗaɓɓugol ɗam."
  18,42,"Dimɗe makko ɗen bonnaa o weeti homo waylita newe makko ɗen e dow ko o nafki kon e mabba, tawi kammba ko fukkiiba e daƴƴe mabba, homo wi'a: "Ee haaniina,hara mi kafidaano e Joomi an hay e gooto"."
  18,43,"Laatanaaki mo fedde nde no walla mo ga Alla, o wonaani poolɗo."
  18,44,"No toon Giggol Alla Goongawol ngol ko Kaŋko moƴƴi mbarjaari moƴƴi battane."
  18,45,"Fiyan ɓe yeru nguurndam aduna ɗam no wa'i wa ndiyam Min njippiniɗam immorde ka kammu jillondiri e majjam puɗi leydi ndin, ɗi wonti munciiɗi keneeli no jarooɗi, Alla wonii ko o kattanɗo e dow kala hu'unde."